headline: Stay Ahead of the Game With PulteGroup (PHM) Q3 Earnings: Wall Street's Insights on Key Metrics
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for PulteGroup (PHM), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended September 2025.
